# Personal Data MCP Server — Hackathon Architecture
**3-hour build · Demo scope · Two-person split**

---

## 1. What We're Building

A **Personal Data Sovereignty System** — a self-hosted MCP server that stores your curated personal profile, paired with a React UI for data entry and profile viewing. Any AI agent can plug in via MCP and query your data with your permission.

**Demo flows (must work end-to-end):**
1. Guided onboarding form → writes to SQLite
2. Profile viewer — reads and displays stored profile
3. MCP agent query demo — Claude queries your MCP server live

