## 3. Data Model

### SQLite — `profile.db`

#### Table: `profile_fields`
```sql
CREATE TABLE profile_fields (
  id          INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
  section     TEXT NOT NULL,   -- e.g. "identity", "professional", "preferences"
  field_key   TEXT NOT NULL,   -- e.g. "full_name", "job_title"
  field_value TEXT,
  data_type   TEXT DEFAULT 'text',  -- text | list | date | number
  source      TEXT DEFAULT 'manual', -- manual | google | facebook
  status      TEXT DEFAULT 'approved', -- approved | pending | rejected
  updated_at  DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE(section, field_key)
);
```

#### Table: `profile_schema`
```sql
CREATE TABLE profile_schema (
  id           INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
  section      TEXT NOT NULL,
  field_key    TEXT NOT NULL,
  label        TEXT NOT NULL,        -- human-friendly label for UI form
  description  TEXT,                 -- hint text shown in form
  data_type    TEXT DEFAULT 'text',
  required     INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  sort_order   INTEGER DEFAULT 0
);
```

### Profile Sections & Fields (Hackathon Scope)

| Section | Fields |
|---|---|
| `identity` | full_name, date_of_birth, location_city, location_country, languages |
| `professional` | job_title, company, industry, years_experience, skills, bio |
| `preferences` | interests, hobbies, communication_style, learning_style |
| `goals` | short_term_goals, long_term_goals, current_focus |
| `context` | timezone, availability, preferred_contact |

