## 5. Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech | Why |
|---|---|---|
| MCP Server | Python + FastMCP | Fastest to get running, clean decorator syntax |
| REST API | FastAPI (same process) | One server, two interfaces |
| Storage | SQLite via `sqlite3` | Zero setup, single file |
| UI | React + Vite | Fast dev server, your friend knows it |
| UI Styling | Tailwind CSS | Fast to prototype |
| HTTP Client (UI) | `fetch` (native) | No extra deps |
| MCP Transport | stdio | Simplest for demo, works with Claude Desktop |

