## 10. What to Skip (Not Worth the 3 Hours)

- Import from Google/Facebook exports — too messy, save for post-hackathon
- Auth / API keys — demo is local, no need
- Curation / approve-reject UI — simplify to manual entry only
- Vector/RAG search — SQLite LIKE search is enough for demo
- Monetization layer — concept only, not built

